<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="glance-n">glance <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɡlɑːns/    美 /ɡlæns/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>一瞥；扫视：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>take</strong> / <strong>have</strong> / <strong>give a glance at</strong>
粗略地看一下</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He saw <strong>at a glance</strong> what had happened.
他一看就知道发生了什么事情。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He fell in love with her <strong>at first glance</strong>.
他对她一见钟情。</p></div></div>